 MOV D,B
 MOV D,C
 MOV D,E
 MOV D,F
 MOV E,A
 MOV E,B
 MOV E,C
 MOV E,D
 MOV E,F
 MOV F,A
 MOV F,B
 MOV F,C
 MOV F,D
 MOV F,E

--MOVE FROM EF TO ACCUMULATOR--
MVS
LVS
;----EF INCREMENT DECREMENT----
INX
DCX 
